{"questionId":"9076969","questionHtml":"<p>The egg comes to rest in a time of 55 ms. Determine the magnitude of the&nbsp;average decelerating force that the ground exerts on the egg.</p>","markschemeHtml":"<p><em><strong>ALTERNATIVE 1:</strong></em></p>\n<p>initial momentum =&nbsp;<em>mv</em>&nbsp;=&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\sqrt {2 \\times 0.058 \\times 0.63} \">\n  <msqrt>\n    <mn>2</mn>\n    <mo>×</mo>\n    <mn>0.058</mn>\n    <mo>×</mo>\n    <mn>0.63</mn>\n  </msqrt>\n</math></span>&nbsp;«= 0.27 kg m s<sup>−1</sup>»</p>\n<p><em><strong>OR</strong></em></p>\n<p><em>mv</em>&nbsp;=&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"0.058 \\times \\sqrt {2 \\times 9.81 \\times 1.1} \">\n  <mn>0.058</mn>\n  <mo>×</mo>\n  <msqrt>\n    <mn>2</mn>\n    <mo>×</mo>\n    <mn>9.81</mn>\n    <mo>×</mo>\n    <mn>1.1</mn>\n  </msqrt>\n</math></span>&nbsp;«= 0.27 kg m s<sup>−1</sup>» ✔</p>\n<p>force =&nbsp;«<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\frac{{{\\text{change in momentum}}}}{{{\\text{time}}}}\">\n  <mfrac>\n    <mrow>\n      <mrow>\n        <mtext>change in momentum</mtext>\n      </mrow>\n    </mrow>\n    <mrow>\n      <mrow>\n        <mtext>time</mtext>\n      </mrow>\n    </mrow>\n  </mfrac>\n</math></span> =»&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\frac{{0.27}}{{0.055}}\">\n  <mfrac>\n    <mrow>\n      <mn>0.27</mn>\n    </mrow>\n    <mrow>\n      <mn>0.055</mn>\n    </mrow>\n  </mfrac>\n</math></span>&nbsp;✔</p>\n<p>4.9&nbsp;«N»&nbsp;✔</p>\n<p><em>F&nbsp;− mg</em>&nbsp;= 4.9 so&nbsp;<em>F&nbsp;</em>= 5.5&nbsp;«N»&nbsp;✔</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><em><strong>ALTERNATIVE 2:</strong></em></p>\n<p>«<em>E</em><sub>k</sub>&nbsp;= <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\frac{1}{2}\">\n  <mfrac>\n    <mn>1</mn>\n    <mn>2</mn>\n  </mfrac>\n</math></span>mv<sup>2</sup>&nbsp;= 0.63 J» v = 4.7&nbsp;m s<sup>−1</sup>&nbsp;✔</p>\n<p>acceleration =&nbsp;«<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\frac{{\\Delta v}}{{\\Delta t}}\">\n  <mfrac>\n    <mrow>\n      <mi mathvariant=\"normal\">Δ</mi>\n      <mi>v</mi>\n    </mrow>\n    <mrow>\n      <mi mathvariant=\"normal\">Δ</mi>\n      <mi>t</mi>\n    </mrow>\n  </mfrac>\n</math></span> =»&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\frac{{4.7}}{{55 \\times {{10}^{ - 3}}}}\">\n  <mfrac>\n    <mrow>\n      <mn>4.7</mn>\n    </mrow>\n    <mrow>\n      <mn>55</mn>\n      <mo>×</mo>\n      <mrow>\n        <msup>\n          <mrow>\n            <mn>10</mn>\n          </mrow>\n          <mrow>\n            <mo>−</mo>\n            <mn>3</mn>\n          </mrow>\n        </msup>\n      </mrow>\n    </mrow>\n  </mfrac>\n</math></span> =&nbsp;«85 m s<sup>−2</sup>»&nbsp;✔</p>\n<p>4.9&nbsp;«N»&nbsp;✔</p>\n<p><em>F&nbsp;− mg</em>&nbsp;= 4.9 so&nbsp;<em>F</em>= 5.5&nbsp;«N»&nbsp;✔</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><em>Accept negative acceleration and force.</em></p>","meta":{"questionId":"9076969","referenceCode":"18N.2.HL.TZ0.3b.ii","subjectId":"46-dp-physics-last-assessment-2024","title":"The egg comes to rest in a time of 55 ms. Determine the magnitude of the average decelerating force that the ground exerts on the egg.","paper":"2","level":"HL","questionNumber":"b.ii","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 4]","breadcrumbLabels":["Core","Core","Topic 2: Mechanics","2.4 – Momentum and impulse","Core","Topic 2: Mechanics"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}}}